Build docker image
docker build -t <account>/mxhcasa:0.0.1 .

Push docker image to Docker Hub
docker image push <account>/mxhcasa:0.9.0

Create network:
docker network create mhxcasenet

Start MySQL in devteria-network
docker run --network mhxcasenet --name mysql -p 3306:3306 -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=Duy12345678@ -d mysql:8.0

Run your application in devteria-network
docker run --name mxhcasa --network mhxcasenet -p 8080:8080 -e DBMS_CONNECTION=jdbc:mysql://mysql:3306/testbase mxhcasa:0.0.1


docker run --name mxhcasa -p 8080:8080 -e DBMS_CONNECTION=jdbc:mysql://172.17.0.2:3306/testbase mxhcasa:0.0.1